  "text": "While there is converging evidence pointing out the increased risk for relapse, affective psychosis and suicide following lithium discontinuation, especially in case of rapid down-titration even after many years of clinical stability of BD [11 -16] , such risk is not fully accounted by the natural course of BD [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
